data.description: Back on the market through no fault of the Seller.  Charming 3 bed, 2 bath single-story home in Wendell, offering a delightful living experience. The open living room design creates a spacious and bright atmosphere, flooded with natural light. Recent upgrades include a new hot water heater, main water line to the house, and fresh carpeting installed in 2022. Since this property is close to downtown you are able to explore this vibrant area of Wendell, which is known for its popularity and abundant attractions.
